# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:3
translate spanish lisalivingroom_acb88e92:

    # "Lisa's not here watching TV like she usually is. What's going on with her?"
    "Lisa no está aquí viendo la tele como suele hacer. ¿Qué le pasa?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:4
translate spanish lisalivingroom_b428ebd3:

    # "I guess she's still upset. Better just give her time."
    "Supongo que sigue enfadada. Mejor darle tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:16
translate spanish lisalivingroom_28820f39:

    # "Lisa is in the living room watching television."
    "Lisa está en el salón viendo la televisión."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:17
translate spanish lisalivingroom_62054172:

    # sp "Hey, honey, I'm just watching some TV. Want to join me?"
    sp "Oye, cariño, estoy viendo un poco la tele. ¿Quieres unirte a mí?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:21
translate spanish lisatv_11b9ab1f:

    # sp "Sure, that sounds great."
    sp "Claro, me parece genial."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:25
translate spanish lisatv_683befdb:

    # "Lisa changes into her nightgown and we go sit in the living room together."
    "Lisa se pone el camisón y nos sentamos juntos en el salón."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:115
translate spanish lisatvconversation_8d017aa1:

    # "I sit down next to her and we watch television together for a while."
    "Me siento a su lado y vemos la televisión juntos un rato."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:117
translate spanish lisatvconversation_3f78d36e:

    # "After the show is over, Lisa looks over to me."
    "Cuando termina el programa, Lisa me mira."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:118
translate spanish lisatvconversation_9938deea:

    # sp "Well, it's getting late. I'm going to go to bed, honey."
    sp "Bueno, se está haciendo tarde. Me voy a la cama, cariño."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:119
translate spanish lisatvconversation_db98731b:

    # pc "Alright, [mom]."
    pc "De acuerdo, [mom]."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:120
translate spanish lisatvconversation_b7fc26cb:

    # sp "Thanks for hanging out with me. Love you."
    sp "Gracias por pasar el rato conmigo. Te quiero."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:121
translate spanish lisatvconversation_776fd6b3:

    # pc "Love you too, [mom]. Good night."
    pc "Yo también te quiero, [mom]. Buenas noches."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:122
translate spanish lisatvconversation_0ffd2107:

    # sp "Good night."
    sp "Buenas noches."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:123
translate spanish lisatvconversation_b9d79178:

    # "She gets up and walks towards her bedroom. I don't really want to watch any more TV, so I turn it off and leave as well."
    "Se levanta y se dirige a su dormitorio. La verdad es que no me apetece seguir viendo la tele, así que la apago y me voy yo también."

